16:43.136 --> 16:44.404
- Hi.
- You see?

16:44.437 --> 16:46.306
You see what I told you?

16:46.339 --> 16:48.441
This is all it took to get
people out on a work night.

16:48.475 --> 16:50.643
- Yup, a lot of people are
shopping and drinking.

16:50.677 --> 16:53.046
I don't even know if we need
to do the open mic part.

16:53.080 --> 16:54.781
- Oh, we need the open mic part.

16:54.814 --> 16:56.249
- Do we?
- Yeah.

16:56.283 --> 16:59.319
- Okay. (Sighs)

16:59.752 --> 17:03.123
- Hey, I think we're going to
uh, get things started here.

17:03.156 --> 17:05.392
(Cheering)
How's everybody doin'?

17:05.425 --> 17:07.394
(Cheering)
Awesome.

17:07.427 --> 17:09.596
Thanks so much for coming to uh,

17:09.629 --> 17:12.232
what I hope will be the first
of many open mic nights

17:12.265 --> 17:14.101
here at the Rose Apothecary.

17:14.134 --> 17:16.803
Um, David and I are so excited
you could all come.

17:16.836 --> 17:19.672
I see everybody's loaded up
on drink tickets.

17:19.706 --> 17:21.441
- Oh yeah.

17:21.474 --> 17:22.642
- That's good news.

17:22.675 --> 17:25.245
I'm going to uh, I guess I'm
gonna get the party started,

17:25.278 --> 17:26.813
