17:31.584 --> 17:34.321
- Okay, this was not my idea.

17:35.455 --> 17:37.257
- All right, um...

17:38.291 --> 17:40.160
I would like to dedicate
this song

17:40.193 --> 17:44.331
to a very special someone
in my life.

17:45.398 --> 17:47.167
David Rose.
- Okay.

17:47.200 --> 17:51.371
- There he is, right there.
That's him. Can't miss him.

17:51.771 --> 17:53.806
- You'll let me know if I
should pull the fire alarm?

17:53.840 --> 17:55.208
